snippet: New York Giants quarterback Eli Manning says older brother Peyton has not talked to him about his playing future this week, adding that the legacy of the Denver Broncos quarterback is set, win or lose Super Bowl 50....
lead_paragraph: New York Giants quarterback Eli Manning says older brother Peyton has not talked to him about his playing future this week, adding that the legacy of the Denver Broncos quarterback is set, win or lose Super Bowl 50.

headline.main: Younger Manning Eli Says Peyton's Legacy Safe, Win or Lose
headline.print_headline: Younger Manning Eli Says Peyton's Legacy Safe, Win or Lose
